data.description: Take a step into this complete remodel. Single-story 1,250 sq.ft. home, 3 Bed / 2 Bath on a 6,480 sq.ft. lot. As you enter this beautifully updated home, the warming colors take your breath away! This open floor plan features hardwood floors. Living room with wood burning fireplace. Updated kitchen, less than a year old kitchen appliances, gas range stove, farmhouse style sink. Dimmable recessed lighting throughout the house. Bedrooms feature custom closets. New roof, two new HVAC split systems, on demand water heater, indoor fire sprinkler system throughout the house, Solar panels, and new plumbing.  This home is the perfect combination between safety, great taste, and tranquility. This home could not be more move-in'' ready!   Add a  lovely landscaping and you have a wonderful forever home.   Located in the desirable Rincon Valley area, in close proximity to prime school district and shopping.
